  "description": {
    "en-US": "Travel phrases for Hong Kong with audio, built for Octopus payments, MTR transfers, airport links, hotel check-ins, and cha chaan teng ordering.",
    "zh-CN": "中国香港旅行短语卡，围绕 Octopus 支付、MTR 换乘、机场快线、酒店入住和茶餐厅点单等高频场景整理。"
  },
  "intro": {
    "en-US": "Built for Hong Kong trips where Airport Express, MTR exits, ferries, hotel counters, and cha chaan tengs all move quickly. These cards help when you need fast Cantonese for Octopus questions, directions inside busy stations, or concise food orders in smaller local spots.",
    "zh-CN": "这套中国香港短语适合那种机场快线、MTR 出入口、渡轮、酒店柜台和茶餐厅会连续出现的旅行节奏。遇到要问 Octopus、在繁忙车站里确认方向，或者在本地小店里快速点单时，短语卡会特别有用。"
  },
  "teaser": {
    "en-US": "Built for Hong Kong Octopus payments, MTR transfers, airport links, and cha chaan teng orders.",
    "zh-CN": "适合中国香港的 Octopus、MTR、机场快线和茶餐厅点单沟通。"
  },
  "travelTips": {
    "en-US": [
      "Keep transport phrases ready for Octopus, MTR exit numbers, and airport transfers because station decisions happen fast in Hong Kong.",
      "Dining phrases are most useful in cha chaan tengs and smaller local spots when you want to order quickly or ask for takeaway.",
      "English works in many tourist-facing places, but a short Cantonese phrase still helps with taxis, neighborhood shops, and busy counters."
    ],
    "zh-CN": [
      "在中国香港，Octopus、MTR 出口编号和机场接驳相关短语最好提前备好，因为很多决定都要在很短时间内完成。",
      "茶餐厅和本地小店里，餐饮短语最实用，尤其适合快速点单或提出外带需求。",
      "很多面向游客的地方可以讲英语，但在出租车、社区小店和繁忙柜台里，几句简短粤语还是会很有帮助。"
    ]
  },
  "highlights": {
    "en-US": [
      "Octopus, MTR, and cha chaan teng orders",
      "Airport Express, ferries, and taxi drop-offs",
      "Hotels, local shops, and concise service requests"
    ],
    "zh-CN": [
      "Octopus、MTR 与茶餐厅点单",
      "机场快线、渡轮与出租车下车点",
      "酒店、本地小店与简短服务沟通"
    ]
  },
